018
019import javax.xml.stream.util.*;
020
021/**
022 * {@link XMLEventAllocator} base class.
023 *
024 * <h5 class='section'>See Also:</h5><ul>
025 *    <li class='link'><a class="doclink" href="https://juneau.apache.org/docs/topics/XmlBasics">XML Basics</a>
